In a large mixing bowl, combine lemon and lime gelatin with boiling water; stir until dissolved. Add cream cheese; let stand for 10 minutes. Beat on high speed until smooth. Stir in milk and mayonnaise. Fold in pineapple. Pour into an ungreased 13-in. x 9-in. x 2-in. dish. Sprinkle with nuts and marshmallows. Cover and refrigerate until set.